<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />那麼這件事<delay20 />就拜託你啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唷！<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay40 />
<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd01" />有找你商量<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />款待新居民的事吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也想幫忙款待新居民那件事，
